speech:
Tata Usaha SD Muhammadiyah Bojonggede Buka Senin s.d. Jum'at pukul 08.00 sampai 14.00 
Apa ada pertanyaan lagi ?

Cara membayar $SPP1 dapat dilakukan di Tata Usaha atau dapat ditransfer melalui rekening sekolah. Rekening SD Muhammadiyah, yaitu BJB a.n SDS Muhammadiyah No. Rekening : 0020726156101. Apabila Anda membayar dengan metode transfer, silakan konfirmasi pembayaran melalui WhatsApp Tata Usaha 0896-5782-5312 (Dimas Eko Saputra).
Apa ada pertanyaan lagi ?

Administration of SD Muhammadiyah Bojonggede Open Monday to Friday 08.00 to 14.00 
Are there any more questions?

How to pay $SPP1 can be done in Administration or can be transferred through a school account. SD Muhammadiyah Account, namely BJB a.n SDS Muhammadiyah Account No. : 0020726156101. If you pay by transfer method, please confirm payment via WhatsApp Administration 0896-5782-5312 (Dimas Eko Saputra).
Are there any more questions?
